
# UI Patterns & Standards

## Component Library
- **shadcn/ui**: Primary component library
- **Tailwind CSS**: Styling framework
- **Lucide React**: Icon library

## Layout Patterns
- **Accordion Layouts**: Use expandable rows instead of grid cards
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach
- **Dark/Light Theme**: Toggle via [ThemeContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/ThemeContext.tsx)

## Table Standards
- **Default Columns**: Day, Installs, D0 ROAS, D7 ROAS
- **Conditional Formatting**: Color-coded cells based on performance
- **Sortable Headers**: Click to sort by column
- **Horizontal Scroll**: Maintain 11pt font size, don't shrink text

## Form Patterns
- **File Upload**: Drag & drop with validation
- **Settings Panel**: Collapsible configuration panel
- **Search/Filter**: Real-time filtering with debounced input

## Navigation
- **Tab-based**: Anasayfa, Müşteriler, Account Managers, Dashboard
- **Breadcrumbs**: Show current location
- **Active States**: Highlight current selection

## Color Scheme
- **Primary**: Blue tones for main actions
- **Success**: Green for positive metrics
- **Warning**: Yellow for neutral metrics  
- **Error**: Red for negative metrics
- **Neutral**: Gray for secondary elements

## File Navigation Behavior
When a file is clicked → automatically navigate to 'overview' tab to show dashboard data.